  "rationale": "<p>Expanding (<i>h</i><i>x</i> + <i>k</i>)(<i>x</i> + <i>j</i>) = <i>h</i><i>x</i>&sup2; + (<i>h</i><i>j</i> + <i>k</i>)<i>x</i> + <i>k</i><i>j</i>. Equating with 6<i>x</i>&sup2; + <i>b</i><i>x</i> + 35 gives <i>h</i> = 6, <i>k</i><i>j</i> = 35, and <i>b</i> = <i>h</i><i>j</i> + <i>k</i>. Since <i>k</i> and <i>j</i> are integers with <i>k</i><i>j</i> = 35, the value 35/<i>k</i> = <i>j</i> is an integer. The other options are not guaranteed to be integers.</p>",
